## Summary
This documentation covers the Amplitude Guides and Surveys Web SDK installation and configuration, including integration with Amplitude Browser SDK, third-party analytics providers (like Segment), and Google Tag Manager, with methods for theme management, localization, router configuration, and programmatic control of guides and surveys.

